Name: Pressure Overdrive
About the game: Step up a gear: Pressure returns with Overdrive! Start your steam buggy and join “La Resistance”...it’s still time to prevent Count Soap from powering his Uber-Spa with stolen water! In Pressure Overdrive you revisit an action packed world, filled with crazy characters and funky humor. This enhanced version will challenge your skills, while you race, ram and blast your way through countless bullets and enemies. Customize your buggy for clever play styles and have a friend join the cause in local coop mode. “La Resistance” counts on you! Improved controls New weapons Single player and local coop Campaign and freeplay mode New endless mode New bossfights 3 worlds with 30+ Levels Dozens of enemy types & 3 bossfights Upgrade your buggy with 35+ items Online highscores 10 languages supported Steamfunky soundtrack included!
